@startuml C4_Code
title C4 Уровень 4 - Код / классы

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class SecureGraphRagAgent {
  .. публичный API ..
  +ingest(document: DocumentInput): IngestionResult
  +answer(request: QueryRequest): QueryResponse
  .. узлы LangGraph ..
  -_guard_input_node(state): dict
  -_retrieve_node(state): dict
  -_graph_expand_node(state): dict
  -_generate_node(state): dict
  -_guard_output_node(state): dict
}

class Guardrails {
  .. проверки безопасности ..
  +inspect_input(text: str): GuardrailResult
  +inspect_output(text: str, allowed_chunks: set, citations: list): GuardrailResult
  +can_read_chunk(user: UserContext, chunk: Chunk): bool
  +redact_pii(text: str): str
}

interface VectorStore {
  .. контракт векторного хранилища ..
  +upsert_chunks(chunks)
  +search(query, user, top_k): list
}

interface GraphStore {
  .. контракт графового хранилища ..
  +upsert_chunks(chunks)
  +expand(seed_chunk_ids, user, limit): list
}

class InMemoryVectorStore
class InMemoryGraphStore
class QdrantVectorStore
class Neo4jGraphStore

class LocalLlmClient {
  .. клиент локального vLLM ..
  +generate(query: str, chunks): str
}

class ExtractiveLlmFallback {
  .. fallback без LLM для smoke-тестов ..
  +generate(query: str, chunks): str
}

class Chunk {
  .. фрагмент документа с ACL ..
  +id: str
  +document_id: str
  +tenant_id: str
  +text: str
  +acl_groups: tuple
  +ordinal: int
  +metadata: dict
  +entities: tuple
}

class QueryRequest {
  +query: str
  +user: UserContext
  +top_k: int
}

class QueryResponse {
  +answer: str
  +citations: tuple
  +blocked: bool
  +guardrail_events: tuple
}

SecureGraphRagAgent --> Guardrails
SecureGraphRagAgent --> VectorStore
SecureGraphRagAgent --> GraphStore
SecureGraphRagAgent --> LocalLlmClient
SecureGraphRagAgent --> QueryRequest
SecureGraphRagAgent --> QueryResponse
VectorStore <|.. InMemoryVectorStore
VectorStore <|.. QdrantVectorStore
GraphStore <|.. InMemoryGraphStore
GraphStore <|.. Neo4jGraphStore
InMemoryVectorStore --> Chunk
InMemoryGraphStore --> Chunk
QdrantVectorStore --> Chunk
Neo4jGraphStore --> Chunk

@enduml
